ays with shedding unnecessary risk we look at risk from both a market perspective and a fund or individual security perspective based on decades of experience and constantly refined proprietary modeling we weigh expected returns against anticipated volatilities we construct and tactically adjust portfolios according to these measurements consistent with your goals and risk appetite spruces diversified portfolios frequently consist of a combination of traditional and alternative asset classes worldwide  a complex and creative construction that we believe will yield attractive results often with less downside risk daily focus on achieving investor goals agility is vital to our success so we keep a vigilant eye on the rapid pace of developments in todays domestic and international markets rebalancing your investments as needed  daily if necessary  to take advantage of subtle changes in climate above all we believe in genuine open partnership and work closely with each of our clients to address their concerns and their longterm goals spruce investment advisors llc one stamford plaza  tresser blvd th floor stamford connecticut  usa     spruce investment advisors llc privacy policy terms  agreements spruce investment advisors llc » investor login contact us log in about us investment approach our clients why spruce careers investor login investors and their advisors in the spruce entities may accessthe secure web portal here for all other users please click here spruce investment advisors llc one stamford plaza  tresser blvd th floor stamford connecticut  usa     spruce investment advisors llc privacy policy terms  agreements spruce investment advisors llc » our clients contact us log in about us investment approach our clients why spruce careers our clients partners in prosperity clients have been drawn to spruce for a variety of reasons but chief among them may be our approach to collaboration we foster true partnerships that surpass the typical clientadvisor relationsh